description: The front-end development scene changes at a lightning pace. You don’t go too long without hearing about a new and upcoming JavaScript library that promises it is going to change everything. name: C++
description: C# is a beautiful cross-platform language that can be used to build different kinds of apps: web apps, mobile apps, desktop apps, and games. The versatility of C# brings you a lot of career options.This course is the ideal starting point for anyone who wants to master the fundamentals of C#.
